textAnnotations.description:
and warm
Their air of smiling somnolence showed them
to have been guests at yesterday's
celebrations, and their friendly welcome
sympathy, as she explained
how she had come to miss the party,
made her send a complacent glance
in Pers' direction. What a fuss-box the
man was, she thought impatantly,
trying
to
worry
her into the belief
that her failure to appear at a function
on the estate was a major error:
N
